{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b3d1689b7c","title":"中央转发邮电部党组关于三反报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"57229750c4","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"b3d1689b7c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"152fc15ce2","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邮电部党组1951年12月7日的三反报告指出，邮电系统的贪污案件，除一般旧社会常有的类型外，尚有与专门业务相结合的专业贪污案，且极为普遍。贪污腐化现象滋长的原因，一是全国解放以后，反贪污反浪费尚未形成广泛深入的群众运动，加之党内生活、政治教育不健全，资本主义反过来引诱与腐蚀我们：二是县邮电局多原封未动，领导方面忽视了县局的改造与加强；三是对惩治贪污犯采取了姑息态度，片面地理解“不能轻易开除人”与“不能造成工人的失业”，客观上助长了资污化的风气。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2f4b78256b","type":"title","text":"中央转发邮电部党组关于三反报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"152fc15ce2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央和军委各部门，中央人民政府各党组，客中央局，并请转发分局，省市区党委，地委和县委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4d32d57a7","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将中央邮电部党组关于反贪污反浪费反官主义报告一件发给你们。因邮电事业普及全国，贪污问题又很严重，故应将此件转发县委，提起大家注意。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d5c400130","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f4efefb8d","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b3d1689b7c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":123,"end":123}}}},